quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  100,1,"M wẽen ne wed-zoets sẽn vʋʋsd vʋʋs-tula (n vʋʋs n sεsdẽ)."
  100,2,"Lɑ M wẽen ne wiidi nins sẽn zoete, tɩ b nɑ-bendã korsdẽ tɩ bug-pãrsã yitã."
  100,3,"Lɑ M wẽen ne wiidi nins sẽn pigd bεεbã yibeoog pigdba."
  100,4,"Tɩ b ruk wubsg zĩigẽ wã."
  100,5,"Tɩ b kẽ (bεεbã) zãmã sʋk ne-ba."
  100,6,"Ad ninsaal yaa sõm-zɩt ne a Soabã."
  100,7,"La ad a yaa kaset-soab ne yẽ sẽn gɩdgd sõmã wã."
  100,8,"La ad a yaa noang-kεgeng soab ne arzεkã."
  100,9,"Rẽ yĩnga a ka nɑ n bãnge, b sã n wa bugs bũmb ning sẽn be yaadẽ wã, (tɩ ɑd yellã pɑ wɑ yẽ sẽn dɑ tẽedã)."
  100,10,"La b vẽneg bũmb nins sẽn be yãadẽ wã."
  100,11,"Ad b Soabã, A yaa Mit ne bãmb raaren-kãngã."
